    <subsubsection xml:id="subsubsec-Preparing-bills">
      <title>Preparing bills</title>
      <activity>
        <p>
         Work in groups
        </p>
        <p>
          Read the story below.
        </p>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                Gillian bought the following items from a kiosk:
              </p>
              <p><m>2\,kg</m> of sugar at <m>sh\,120</m> per kilogram</p>
              <p><m>2</m> loaves of bread at <m>sh\, 50</m> per loaf</p>
              <p><m>5</m> packets of milk at <m>sh\, 50</m> per packet</p>
              <p><m>3</m> packets of salt at <m>sh\, 20</m> per packet.</p>
              <p>She paid for the items using a thousand shillings note.</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>
